<p corresp='TTP32303416P2' xml:id='OTP32303416P2'>This is the entire voting population of this Township with the exception of Four, Two absent and Two to whom it has not been presented <del rend='overstrike'>to</del>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32303416P3' xml:id='OTP32303416P3'>The Petitioners respe-ctfully presents their compliments to Messr. <rs ref='#S95611'>Johnston</rs> and <rs ref='#S32033562'>Buck</rs> their Representatives and [unclear]—able Consideration
</p>

